AgileWizard use Rake as build tool and ruby as language for build script. Documentation of Rake at http://docs.rubyrake.org/
Ruby 1.9.2 and albacore are equired.
Please download ruby from http://rubyinstaller.org/.

If neccesary, please install ruby devkit from http://rubyinstaller.org/ as well. And you can find find the installing wiki at https://github.com/oneclick/rubyinstaller/wiki/Development-Kit.

How to install albacore after installing ruby:
gem install albacore

Note: No blank char allowed in ruby installed directory, or you can not install ruby extension 'jekyll'.